      "source": "#### JEP 522 â€” G1 GC: Improve Throughput by Reducing Synchronization\n\nThis notebook creates GC pressure to let you observe behavior and throughput under G1. Use `-Xlog:gc` when running from CLI for detailed logs and compare across builds.\n\nReferences:\n- JEP 522: https://openjdk.org/jeps/522\n",
